---
title: Louisiana Baked Lamb Rump with Herb-Roasted Veggies, Slaw & Dill-Parsley Mayo
description: Load up lamb rump with flavour before baking it until golden and tender. Smokey, southern-inspired, Louisiana spice
blend and a creamy dill-parsley slaw will combine to make a sensational dinner that everyone will happily devour!
